      <h2>Our Guarantee</h2>
      <p>At Max Labs, we stand behind the quality of our products. If you're not completely satisfied with your purchase for any reason, we offer a hassle-free 30-day money-back guarantee.</p>
      
      <h2>Return Eligibility</h2>
      <p>To be eligible for a return, the following conditions must be met:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Request must be made within 30 days of receiving your order</li>
        <li>Products must be in their original packaging</li>
        <li>At least 50% of the product must remain unused</li>
        <li>Proof of purchase (order number or receipt) is required</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>How to Request a Return</h2>
      <p>Follow these simple steps to initiate a return:</p>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Contact Us:</strong> Email support@maxlabs.com or call 1-800-MAX-LABS with your order number and reason for return</li>
        <li><strong>Receive Authorization:</strong> Our team will provide you with a Return Merchandise Authorization (RMA) number and return shipping instructions</li>
        <li><strong>Ship Your Return:</strong> Pack the items securely and ship them to the address provided</li>
        <li><strong>Receive Your Refund:</strong> Once we receive and inspect your return, we'll process your refund within 5-7 business days</li>
      </ol>
      
      <h2>Refund Process</h2>
      <p>Once your return is received and inspected:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>You will receive an email notification confirming receipt of your return</li>
        <li>Refunds are processed within 5-7 business days</li>
        <li>Refunds are issued to the original payment method</li>
        <li>Depending on your bank or credit card company, it may take an additional 5-10 business days for the refund to appear on your statement</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>Return Shipping</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Defective or Incorrect Items:</strong> We will provide a prepaid return shipping label at no cost to you</li>
        <li><strong>Change of Mind:</strong> Customer is responsible for return shipping costs</li>
        <li>We recommend using a trackable shipping method for your protection</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>Exchanges</h2>
      <p>If you'd like to exchange a product for a different item:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Contact our customer support team to initiate an exchange</li>
        <li>We'll ship your new item once we receive your return</li>
        <li>If there's a price difference, we'll either charge or refund the difference</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>Damaged or Defective Products</h2>
      <p>If you receive a damaged or defective product:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Contact us within 48 hours of receiving your order</li>
        <li>Include photos of the damage or defect</li>
        <li>We will send a replacement at no additional cost</li>
        <li>No need to return the damaged product in most cases</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>Non-Returnable Items</h2>
      <p>The following items cannot be returned:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Products that have been opened and more than 50% consumed</li>
        <li>Products purchased more than 30 days ago</li>
        <li>Gift cards</li>
        <li>Items marked as "Final Sale"</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>Cancellations</h2>
      <p>If you need to cancel an order:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Contact us immediately at support@maxlabs.com</li>
        <li>Orders can be cancelled if they haven't been shipped yet</li>
        <li>If your order has already shipped, you'll need to follow the return process</li>
      </ul>
      
